"text", "text": ".] And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstdAmhu", "text_ar": "استدامهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He acted with moderation, gently, deliberately,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "leisurely, in it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, M, K, TA;) namely, an affair, or a case: (S:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sought, desired, asked,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "demanded, its continuance,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "long continuance,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "endless continuance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dAwmhu", "text_ar": "داومهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K, TA) in both of these senses: (K, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he asked him to render"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a thing"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "continual"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.: (Mgh, Msb, TA:) and also (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he acted gently and deliberately in it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "namely, an affair, or a case: (Msb:) and (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he acted gently with him;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Fr, T in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "dym", "text_ar": "ديم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", M, Msb, Kt;) i. e., another person, (Msb,) or his creditor; as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AisotadomaAhu", "text_ar": "اِسْتَدْمَاهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Fr, T, M, K,) which we judge to be formed from the former by transposition, because we do not find it [in this sense] to have any inf. n. (M.) A poet says, (T, S, Msb,) namely, Keys Ibn-Zuheyr, (S,)"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "falaA taEojalo biA^amorika waA@sotadimohu\n                      \n                      ↓ \n      famaA Sal~aY EaSaAka kamusotadiymi"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, S, Msb,) i. e. (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Therefore haste not in thine affair, but act with moderation, gently, deliberately,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "leisurely, therein"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "];"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "for no one has straightened thy staff by turning it round over the fire,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T,) meaning, no one has managed thine affair soundly,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like one who acts with moderation,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (T, Msb.) And another says, (S,) namely, Mejnoon, (TA,)"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "waA_in~aY EalaY layolaY lazaArK waA_in~aniY\n                      \n                     \n                        EalaY*aAka fiymaA bayonanaA A^asotadiymuhaA"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning (assumed tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And verily I am blaming Leylà; and verily, notwithstanding that,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I look for her aiding me by good conduct"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the matter that is between us"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asotadiymu A@ll~`ha", "text_ar": "اَسْتَدِيمُ ا@للّٰهَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "niEomataka", "text_ar": "نِعْمَتَكَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I seek,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "desire,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ask, of God the continuance,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "long continuance,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "endless continuance, of thy favour,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the like."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Mgh, TA. *) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asotadiymu A@ll~`ha Eiz~aka", "text_ar": "اَسْتَدِيمُ ا@للّٰهَ عِزَّكَ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I ask God to continue,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "continue long,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thy might,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "power,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c. (Msb.) The phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AstdAm lubosa Alv~awobi", "text_ar": "استدام لُبْسَ الثَّوْبِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He continued long the wearing of the garment,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he did not hasten to pull off the garment,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "may be from the saying"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aisotadamotu EaAqibapa AlA^amori", "text_ar": "اِسْتَدَمْتُ عَاقِبَةَ الاَمْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I looked,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "watched,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "waited, for the end,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "issue,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "result, of the affair,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "case."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.)       -A3-  Also"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a man)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "stooped his head, blood dropping from it:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "formed by transposition from"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AisotadomaY", "text_ar": "اِسْتَدْمَى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Kr, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["T", "Sb", "TA", "Sh", "S", "M", "K", "Mgh", "Msb", "Fr"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}